data.description: This immaculate, expanded split level sparkles with pride of ownership inside and out.  From the welcoming curb appeal and lovely expanded driveway with paver outline to the living room with vaulted ceilings, luxury vinyl flooring throughout, large updated kitchen overlooking side yard and renovated bathrooms. This home is sure to check off many items on your "wish list"  The sun filled feeling of the home is quite special and and must be experienced in person.  Also notable recently renovated den, recessed lighting throughout, level fenced yard, young CAC + Roof, and so much more! This home is one of the few split levels in the area that offers an additional basement space and garage. Energy efficient home run with natural gas heat and leased solar panels Get ready to fall in love!
